                        <li>10.	<b><u>Dispute resolution:</u></b> I agree that in the event of any dispute or uncertainty, I will let Credit Provider know in writing, and if the dispute is not resolved, I may take the matter up with the National Credit Regulator at toll share number 0860 100 406.</li>
                        <li>11.	<b><u>Administration order:</u></b> I declare that I am not under administration, nor am I going to apply for an administration order. If I am placed under administration after entering into this Agreement, I agree that all instalments still due after the administration order is granted, fall within the ambit of Section 74 A (2)(e)(ii) of the Magistrates Court Act and are excluded in terms of Section 74 C (2) of the said act and the Credit Provider will be able to recover all moneys still outstanding in terms of this Agreement by legal action.</li>
                        <li>12.	<b><u>Debt counselling:</u></b> I may apply to a debt counsellor to be declared over indebted in terms of section 86 of the Act. I can access the names of debt counsellors at www.ncr.org.za.</li>

                    </ul>
